  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "</b> </i>] [<i>Authorizes</i>]<b> Requires</b> the State Treasurer to [<i>loan</i>]<b> use</b> up to [<i>20 percent of</i>] <b>$44 million from </b>the Unclaimed Property and Estates Fund to <b>guarantee a loan made to a</b> rural [<i>hospitals</i>]<b> hospital</b> for financial stabilization. Declares an emergency, effective on passage."
    }
